Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.00,0:00:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 表演时间到 - 我刚跟希亚拍完《蜜汁男孩2》\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Showtime. - I just shot Honey Boy 2 with Shia.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.25,0:00:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,闻起来像阿贝克隆比零售店 被711便利店给上了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Smells like an Abercrombie got fucked by a 7-Eleven.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.34,0:00:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那是牛奶吗  - 爽死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Is that milk? -  Heavens to Betsy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.80,0:00:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- 那就加入吧 乐趣多多哦 - 我可是跟加里布塞玩过三人行的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You can join the fun. - And I've had a threesome with Gary Busey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.59,0:00:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,（前情提要）\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You left us for dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.76,0:00:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,扔下我们 见死不救 现在居然装作什么都没发生过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and now it's like nothing happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.06,0:00:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我会杀了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll fucking kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.85,0:00:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 来啊 开枪啊 - 去他妈的布彻尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Go on. Do it. - Fuck Butcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.31,0:00:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- 去他妈的休伊 - 你只会把我们全部人拖下水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Fuck Hughie. - You're just gonna drag us all down with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.23,0:00:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- 妈妈 你好 - 安妮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Mom! Annie. - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.07,0:00:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你让沃特给我注射药物的时候 我几岁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How old was I when you let Vought pump me full of drugs?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.82,0:00:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他们承诺 你将有机会过上非凡的人生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They promised that you'd have a chance at an extraordinary life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.95,0:00:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你告诉我爸爸离开 是因为他亏掉了我们所有的积蓄\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You told me that Daddy left because he lost all of our savings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.37,0:00:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是因为投资失败吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Was it really bad investments?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.24,0:00:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你的猛男秀都是装样子的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your whole Marlboro Man act, it's fucking crap, and I--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.91,0:00:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,和谐堡是一家陆军医院 沃特就是在那里试验一代五号的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fort Harmony was an Army hospital where Frederick Vought was testing the V1.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.92,0:00:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,如果还有剩下的药剂 那就一定要去那里找\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If there's any more left out there, that would be the fucking place to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.59,0:00:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,一代五号的药力强上十倍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}V1's ten times more potent than today's formula.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.30,0:00:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,只在早期的几个超人类身上起了效\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Only worked on a handful of early Supes:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.01,0:00:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你和风暴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you and Stormfront.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.39,0:01:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谁是风暴  - 沃特博士的妻子 叫克拉拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-  Who is Stormfront? -  Dr. Vought's wife Clara.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.97,0:01:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你是认识自由女的吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think you knew her as Liberty?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.68,0:01:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我们仍要去对付祖国人 对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're still gonna go after Homelander, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.93,0:01:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,没有病毒怎么去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not without the virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.35,0:01:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你说我足够强大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You said I was strong enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.60,0:01:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你说只有我才能阻止他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You said I was the only one who could stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.15,0:01:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我那样说好让你叫他离开沃特塔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just said that so you'd get him out of the tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.73,0:01:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我的乖孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My sweet, sweet boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.28,0:01:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,祖国人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Homelander?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.75,0:01:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,鞭…炮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fire... cracker.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.42,0:01:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,有股什么味儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's that smell?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.58,0:01:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是我新的香水产品线\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, it, uh, might be my new perfume line.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.88,0:01:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,叫“李将军的秘密”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's General Lee's Secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.55,0:01:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.05,0:01:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是我父亲 士兵男孩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's my father. It's Soldier Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我闻得出 你浑身都是他的气味 - 对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Uh, I can smell him all over you. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.85,0:01:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,当然是这样 因为我们刚刚在为采访做准备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course. 'Cause we was just, uh, prepping for our interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.39,0:01:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,准备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Prepping?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.57,0:01:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这个嘛…我需要你做件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh... I need you for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.32,0:01:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.91,0:02:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我得到了最绝妙的信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have received the most wonderful message.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.79,0:02:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,一个天使…下凡来找我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was visited... by an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.79,0:02:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,她预言了我的命运\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And she foretold my destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.88,0:02:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 赞美我主 您的命运是什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wow. Well, praise be. And what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.80,0:02:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,神\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}God.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.26,0:02:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,先生 那太棒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sir, that is wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.18,0:02:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,侍奉我主是最崇高的使命了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is no higher calling than serving the Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.72,0:02:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不是“侍奉我主”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Not serving the Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.02,0:02:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,而是成为主\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Being the Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.36,0:02:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是弥赛亚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am the Messiah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.53,0:02:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是救世主\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm the savior of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.03,0:02:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,弥…赛亚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The... Messiah?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.58,0:02:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.12,0:02:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,祝贺您\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Congrats.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.08,0:02:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.34,0:02:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直都知道自己很特别 我就知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I always knew I was special. I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.92,0:03:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我受过苦 我品尝过艰难困苦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I suffered. I suffered so many hardships, and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.51,0:03:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,而我…不明白为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I couldn't understand why.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.64,0:03:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但你…你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you... you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直都心知肚明…不是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you always saw it. Didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.10,0:03:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直都知道我很特别\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You knew all along I was special.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.23,0:03:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我才选择让你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is why I have chosen you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.44,0:03:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,来传扬我即将成为真神的消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to spread the word of my coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么传扬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.28,0:03:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我们控制着地球上最强大的媒体机构\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, we control the most powerful media apparatus on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.83,0:03:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的宣传 耶稣也望尘莫及\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jesus would kill for our marketing. Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得如何\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.01,0:03:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,您知道的 我会为您做任何事 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you know I would do anything for you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.43,0:03:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1}《英雄克星》\N第五季第四集
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs21}本WEB版外挂字幕由  {\c&H9B30FF&}风吹来的那片云{\c&HFFFFFF&}  双语合并
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.15,0:03:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,他醒了 起死回生了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, here he is. Back from the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,慢点 慢慢来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Easy does it. Easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.45,0:04:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,给\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.75,0:04:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,有点像《星球大战5：帝国反击战》 不是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a bit like that Empire Strikes Back film, innit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没看过那部 - 什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Uh, never saw it. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.38,0:04:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- 胡说 我给你看过 - 没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Bollocks. I showed it to you. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.09,0:04:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你给我看过《星球大战》 可妈妈一集也不让我看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You showed me Star Wars. And Mom never let me watch any of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.89,0:04:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,里面有 演《意外的人生》那家伙 对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're with that guy from Regarding Henry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.02,0:04:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,总之 电影里有这么一幕\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anyway, there's this bit, see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.19,0:04:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,年轻的卢克跳进自己的飞船\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Young Luke hops in his spaceship,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.69,0:04:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,去找自己的老爸达斯维德理论\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}fucks off to a barney with his old man Darth Vader.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.19,0:04:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他收到了… - 等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Cops-- - Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.48,0:04:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,达斯维德是天行者卢克的爸爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Darth Vader's Luke Skywalker's dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.82,0:04:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,对 有点透露剧情了 不过 听着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. It's a bit of a spoiler. But, anyway, listen,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.45,0:04:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,重点是你应该 等我们解决了病毒的问题再去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the point is you should've waited till we got the virus sorted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.24,0:04:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这是战争\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.66,0:04:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,而你是我们最强大的武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you're the best weapon we got.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.29,0:04:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,可要是害自己进了运尸袋 你就对谁都没有用处了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you ain't no use to anyone if you go put yourself into a body bag
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.17,0:05:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你得先把祖国人弄进运尸袋才行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}fore we put Homelander in one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,至少我有足够的胆量去尝试\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At least I was brave enough to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.97,0:05:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,孩子 勇敢和愚蠢之间只有一线之隔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, there's a fine line between bravery and stupidity, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你才他妈的不在乎我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't give a shit about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.89,0:05:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你从来都没在乎过我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe you never did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我去再给你拿点水来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here. I'll fetch you some more water.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.20,0:05:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的青少年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fucking teenagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.55,0:05:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 牛人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Welcome back, motherfucker.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.19,0:05:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.03,0:06:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.12,0:06:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.04,0:06:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,有型有款嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Check you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.17,0:06:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,- 谢谢 - 好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Thank you, thank you. -  All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.63,0:06:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你们这群傻蛋搞完“时装周”了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you twats are all done with Fashion Week,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,那就开工吧 好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}let's get to work, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.09,0:06:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,法兰奇 我们需要多久 准备出足够的病毒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Frenchie, how long till we got a dose big enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.59,0:06:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下的病毒很少 需要时间繁殖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, there was so little virus left. It needs time to multiply.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.68,0:06:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道他们都是怎么说的吧  小火慢炖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know what they say, huh? Cook low and slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.43,0:06:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,要他妈的多久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How fucking long?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 至少几周 - 好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Weeks, at least. - Okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们现在就应该去和谐堡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}then we should go to Fort Harmony now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.43,0:06:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那里80年前就被关闭了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That place got shut down 80 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.10,0:06:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,如果那里有剩余的一代五号 也不会很容易就找到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If there's any V1 left in there, it ain't gonna be easy to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,还有个“小”问题 那里可能 会有被五号感染的畜生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And there is also the small matter of the likely V'ed-up beast
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.11,0:06:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,让那些童子军的内脏溢了出来 就像吉百利奶油夹心蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that spilled those Boy Scouts' innards like a Cadbury à la crème, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.57,0:06:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要提醒你们 斯坦埃德加在祖国人手上吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do I need to remind you guys that Homelander has Stan Edgar?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.24,0:06:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,很可能他们早已做好了充分的准备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Odds are they're ten steps ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.20,0:06:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们先得到一代五号 就能救安妮 救喜美子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If we get the V1 first, we save Annie, we save Kimiko,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.20,0:06:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,救你 如果你在乎的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we save you. If you give a shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.83,0:07:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,要是祖国人得到了 他就会长生不老\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If Homelander gets it, he's immortal,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,病毒就没用了 我们就惨了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}virus is useless, and we're fucked sideways.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.25,0:07:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 谁想去…克利尔菲尔德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, who wants to go to... Clearfield?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.17,0:07:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,谁来照顾莱恩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who's gonna take care of Ryan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.26,0:07:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,他走了 没打招呼就走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's gone. He legged it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.22,0:07:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道是谁的错呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wonder whose fault that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.47,0:07:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,伙计 要是我的话 就不会胡乱指责\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I wouldn't be throwing stones if I were you, mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你能告诉我们星光在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Unless you can tell us where Starlight is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.86,0:07:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我们赶快行动吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right. Let's get cracking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.54,0:07:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Annie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 我得跟你谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, listen, I need to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.72,0:07:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我洗耳恭听\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm all ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.64,0:07:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 你能别扫雪了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, can you please stop doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.90,0:08:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么找到我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How did you find me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.19,0:08:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经找了好几个月了 你很擅长躲藏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've been looking for months. You are really good at hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.44,0:08:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,已经20年不见了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It has been 20 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.07,0:08:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,可你跟我说的第一件事居然是这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and that's the first thing that you have to say to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该说什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What should I say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.45,0:08:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,爸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.71,0:08:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮 这是你弟弟…梅森\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Annie, this is your brother... Mason.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.01,0:08:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,很简单 总统先生 您取消对公立学校的资助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's simple, Mr. President. You defund the public schools
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.51,0:08:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,将款项付给祖国人自由学院\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and give vouchers for the Homelander Freedom Academies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.55,0:08:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,您不想让孩子们读到同性恋企鹅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't want kids reading about gay penguins
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.26,0:08:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,或者变成觉醒的圣战分子 对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and becoming woke jihadis, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢您 先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.48,0:08:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我说清楚 我不吃“召你前去”这套\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me be clear. Nobody summons me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.77,0:08:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,上次指挥我的黑人女性还是内尔卡特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The last time I let a Black woman boss me around, it was Nell Carter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.53,0:08:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我戴着阴茎环 准备了一浴缸的科瑞起酥油\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With a cock ring and a tub of Crisco.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.74,0:08:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,业务分析师警告说 协议里有一项会影响你获得电影签约\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}B.A. flagged a deal point for your movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.24,0:09:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能给你的拖车提供… “一大碗可卡因”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We cannot furnish your trailer with, quote, "a big bowl of cocaine."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.75,0:09:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我的附加条款里都写了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's in my rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那些条款是1984年签的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From 1984.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.37,0:09:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为自己可以为所欲为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think I can have whatever the fuck I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.33,0:09:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管去找祖国人谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're welcome to take it up with Homelander.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.71,0:09:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,等他从和谐堡回来 你就可以去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When he gets back from Fort Harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.09,0:09:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,和谐堡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fort Harmony?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.22,0:09:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,祖国人和斯坦埃德加 进行了一番坦诚的对话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Homelander and Stan Edgar had a good heart-to-heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们认为 很有可能在和谐堡找到一代五号\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and we think there's a strong chance of finding V1 at Fort Harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.60,0:09:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,沃特博士不就是在那里 给你们进行首批注射的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Isn't that where Dr. Vought first injected you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.31,0:09:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这是好消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's great news.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.44,0:09:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,如果祖国人找到了它 就会对病毒免疫 跟你一样长生不老\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If he finds it, Homelander will be immune to the virus and immortal, like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你们就会永远相伴 永远都是…父子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'll get to spend eternity together. Father and son. Forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.37,0:09:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 他什么时候离开的  - 还没离开呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- When did he leave? - Hasn't left yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你可以跟他一起去 告诉他去哪里找\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe you could go with him, show him where to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.92,0:09:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟 有谁比你更了解那个地方呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}After all, who knows that place better than you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.15,0:10:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,很奇怪 没有鸟或动物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's weird. No birds or animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.52,0:10:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- 好像… - 地狱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It's like-- -  Fucking hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.03,0:10:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你就非要把车停得那么远 是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Had to park on the other side of the state, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.99,0:10:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,要是走不了远路 为什么不系好靴子 混蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, if the hike's too hard, why don't you try tying your boots, motherfucker.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,干她娘的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, fuck that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.83,0:10:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,她娘不是我喜欢的类型 小子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not really my type, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.13,0:10:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- 放尊重点好吧  - 布彻尔 知道吧 休伊说得对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hey, how about showing a little respect? - You know, Hughie's right, Butcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.67,0:10:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该先带她出去吃晚饭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should take her out to dinner first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.18,0:10:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,看看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ah, let's see here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.97,0:10:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,根据腐烂的情况 尸体暴露在这里有些时日了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Based on the decomp, these bodies have been here a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.89,0:10:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么东西将他们弄得支离破碎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Something ripped them apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.64,0:10:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是什么杀掉了那些童子军 很可能还在这片树林里隐伏跟踪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whatever killed those Boy Scouts might still stalk these woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.60,0:10:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's get a move on, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.52,0:10:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来这可不是要被大脚怪杀掉的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Didn't come out here to get bummed by Bigfoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.08,0:11:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪 真好吃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Goddamn. This is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么等了这么久才尝  我之前在担心什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why'd I wait so long to try this? What was I worried about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.08,0:11:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,将生命献给我 也许是一条鱼的最高荣誉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Probably the highest honor a fish can have, giving their lives to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.05,0:11:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我敢打赌它们跟47条 处女金枪鱼一起进了鱼的天堂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I bet they go to little fish heaven, with 47 virgin tuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.38,0:11:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 搞什么 兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yo. What the fuck, bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.05,0:11:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我信任你来着 - 所以你现在会讲话了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I trusted you. - Oh, so now you can talk, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.64,0:11:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为使用方法派演技很容易吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You think going full method is easy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.35,0:11:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道不说话有多难吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you know how hard it's been to not talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.31,0:11:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我最强有力的表演手段 可我却不能使用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My most powerful instrument, and I can't even use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.23,0:11:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 我十分投入 我为这个角色奉献了一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I fucking committed. I have given everything to this role,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.90,0:11:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,而你却毫不顾忌地坑害我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you straight up fucked me over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.52,0:11:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 你还在 因为抓来斯坦埃德加而生我的气吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait, are you still butthurt about me bringing in Stan Edgar?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.15,0:11:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为我们是朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought we were friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,每次人们嘲笑你有多蠢 你的超能力是个笑话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had your back every time people laughed at how stupid you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.45,0:11:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你有多傻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}how your powers are a joke,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.95,0:11:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,需要法庭指定的守卫时 我都支持你来着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}how you're so dumb you need a court-appointed guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 没人说这种话 - 很多人都在说 总说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Nobody says that. - Yes, they do. All the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.29,0:11:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我们别把这事 搞成联邦案件 黑人小子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, let's not make a federal case out of this, Bro V. Wade.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.37,0:11:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要得到祖国人的赏识 抓埃德加帮我得到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I needed a win from Homelander. Edgar was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.67,0:11:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是个狗狗的世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a doggy dog world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.05,0:11:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你想说的是狗咬狗吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that what you think the phrase is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:12:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,无所谓 快把你的面具戴上吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whatever. Just... put your fucking mask back on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.80,0:12:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,所以就是这样了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh. So that's how it is, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.09,0:12:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你最好小心着点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You better watch your fucking back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.72,0:12:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 你要怎样报复呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, yeah? What are you gonna do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.35,0:12:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,看见我抓到埃德加 祖国人很高兴 他现在很器重我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Homelander's stoked about Edgar. He loves me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.31,0:12:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,会延续多久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How long is that gonna last?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.56,0:12:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的觉得对他来说 你比他亲爸还重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You really think you're more important to him than his own father?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.90,0:12:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我要把你的屁眼儿全撑开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Open your asshole wider.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.21,0:12:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪 我从后面看 这景象太疯狂了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, man. The view from back here was crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.38,0:12:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.75,0:12:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.80,0:12:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你的超人类尖叫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your super scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.30,0:12:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得给你弄一个更结实的堵嘴球\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We really got to get you a stronger ball gag.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.09,0:12:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你惩罚我罪恶小穴的方法那么狠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The way you punish my sin pit,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.14,0:12:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,什么堵嘴球都不够结实\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}ain't no ball gag in the world strong enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我得说 智者姐妹说 我应该嫁给你以取悦公众的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got to say, when Sage said I should marry you for the optics,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.69,0:12:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我没等她说完就把电话挂了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hung up on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.77,0:12:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但我真的很喜欢精液\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I do love busting gushers...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.28,0:13:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,强有力地射在你那可悲的臭脸上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...all over your pathetic worm face.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.86,0:13:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Aw, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.75,0:13:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,该死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.26,0:13:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我得走了 我忘了要跟敬拜团队开会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got to run. I forgot I have a-a meeting with the Worship Team.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.09,0:13:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他在说谎 教会破产了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's lying. The church is bankrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.59,0:13:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,- 等等 什么 教会破产了  - 什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Wait, what? The church is bankrupt? - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.26,0:13:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,谁…后背艾诗丽告诉你的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who... Did Back Ashley tell you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.47,0:13:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,亏我还对她暗送秋波呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}After all that hot eye contact I was giving her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.73,0:13:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这个吃里扒外的婊子 - 这种大型教会怎么会赔钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- That two-faced bitch. - How do you lose money on a megachurch?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的收入有上亿美元 并且不交税\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You bring in hundreds of millions and don't pay taxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.52,0:13:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,来教会的人减少 捐款在下降\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Attendance is down. Donations are drying up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.44,0:13:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我很确定那两架湾流飞机开销巨大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I'm sure the two Gulfstreams don't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.49,0:13:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,- 亏空有多少  - 就…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- How deep in the hole are you? - Just, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.82,0:13:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- 一点五个亿 - 天哪 你在开玩笑吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- 150 million. - Jesus Christ. Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.99,0:13:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你本应该帮我得到12个百分点的增长 加上福音派的教众\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were supposed to get me a 12-point bump with evangelicals,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.54,0:13:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是让我参加国会的传讯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}not hauled before Congress.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.79,0:13:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才你不还说喜欢 精液强有力地射在我的脸上吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened to how much you love busting gushers on my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.83,0:14:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那是在你把我害得身败名裂之前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That was before you turned me into Tammy fucking Faye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这种情况会招来道德委员会 传票\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is ethics committees, subpoenas.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.55,0:14:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,克里斯海耶斯将会采取行动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Chris Hayes is gonna have a field day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.13,0:14:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, what are we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.80,0:14:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,“我们” 不如你告诉我好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We? You tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.72,0:14:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈的是上帝的使者嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're the fucking emissary of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,女士 您有访客\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ma'am, you have a visitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.52,0:14:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你们帮我个忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need y'all's help with something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.94,0:14:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪 闻起来像做华夫饼的面糊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dang. Smells like a wet shit in a Waffle House in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.99,0:14:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,看见祖国人那个傻屌了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Any sign of super cunt?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.49,0:14:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,可能已经进去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Could already be inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.66,0:14:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那…我们就去看看吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, let's find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.96,0:14:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.33,0:14:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Annie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.38,0:14:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,她会回来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She'll come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.92,0:14:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我都差点没命了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. I almost died.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.96,0:14:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但她想的还是自己 然后腾空而去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But she made it all about her and she took off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.38,0:14:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 去年我被变形者侵犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, last year, I got bad-touched by a shape-shifter,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.09,0:14:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,可她还是千方百计地只想着自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and she still found a way to make it about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.26,0:14:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,她有时候真是个自私的贱人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She can be such a fucking bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.98,0:15:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪 对不起 我…没想说这么刻薄的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jesus, sorry, I-I didn't mean for that to come out so harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.54,0:15:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,该死的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fucking hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.67,0:15:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这他妈的是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fuck happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.54,0:15:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这个被五号感染的畜生 吃了餐前点心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our V'd-up beast enjoyed an amuse-bouche, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.05,0:15:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这就解释了为什么 我们之前没听见动物的动静\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, explains why we didn't hear no animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.30,0:15:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我十分钟之前就说过这话了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said that ten minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.32,0:15:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,（我们家相信祖国人）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.91,0:15:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你好 我是凯西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hi. Kathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.87,0:15:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直都想…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have always wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.41,0:16:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,- 终于见到你了 很开心 - 所以你知道这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It's nice to finally meet you. - So, you knew about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.54,0:16:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,知道嘛 很有意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know what's funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.17,0:16:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我请你去沃特乐园 肯定请了上百次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I must have asked you, like, a hundred times to go to Voughtland,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.09,0:16:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但你总说坐过山车会让你恶心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but you always said the roller coasters would make you nauseous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他这么说的吗 他上去就不想下来呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He said that? Couldn't get him off that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.35,0:16:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你妈怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How's your mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.56,0:16:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,她还好 她在躲藏 但她还好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's okay. She's in hiding, but she's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.48,0:16:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你是警察吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're a cop?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.56,0:16:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 警官 - 警官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Deputy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我还以为你在电话公司上班呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thought you were working for, um, the telephone company.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.20,0:16:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你有多久没看见投币电话了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When's the last time you saw a pay phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.16,0:16:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 当警察意味着 你在逮捕星光追随者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, does that mean you're rounding up Starlighters?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.49,0:16:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说恐怖分子吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You mean terrorists?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.04,0:16:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 梅森  - 对不起 我很粗鲁吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Mason. -  Sorry, am I being rude?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.29,0:16:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,在我们家客厅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're all good with
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.37,0:16:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,给超人类连环杀手上茶 我们对此都毫无异议吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}serving tea to the Supe serial killer in our living room?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,够了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.55,0:16:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,知道吗 我很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know what? I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.80,0:16:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 我来这里 就已经让你们身处险境了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry, I've put you guys in danger just by being here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.22,0:16:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,对我只字不提 你这么做是对的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were right keeping me a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.93,0:16:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我走就是了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.72,0:17:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮 等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Annie, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.56,0:17:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我在做酸奶牛肉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm making a stroganoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.85,0:17:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是预制菜来的 不过 跟我们一起吃晚餐吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, it's Hamburger Helper, but... Have dinner with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.56,0:17:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,去洗洗衣服 洗个澡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wash your clothes, take a shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.52,0:17:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,无意冒犯 不过…你应该洗个澡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No offense, but you could use one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.95,0:17:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,真是疯了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.87,0:17:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,没搞错吧  午饭又吃门多西诺农场快餐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Really? We're getting fucking Mendo for lunch again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.75,0:17:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,巴哈绿女神酱蔬菜沙拉 配仿西班牙辣香肠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Baja Green Goddess with Impossible Chorizo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.58,0:17:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,能不能叫人去趟家得宝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, can someone make a run to Home Depot
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.13,0:17:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,给我买点有机泥炭土  1.4公斤 谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and get me some organic peat moss soil? Three pounds? Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.25,0:17:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 各位 继续吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, y'all. Let's keep it going.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.55,0:17:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,畅所欲言 什么想法都欢迎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Blue sky day. No bad ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.84,0:17:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,只需要让大家信服 祖国人是我们的救世主\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just got to sell Homelander as our Lord and savior is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.05,0:17:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 这只是个初步的想法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right, I first thought theater,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.64,0:17:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 他在电视直播上 创造奇迹怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but what if he performed a miracle on live TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他可以分开红海之水 将难民送回原籍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He could part the Red Sea and send some refugees back where they came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.69,0:17:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 在电视直播上做不到 这些都得用视觉特效做出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, you couldn't do it live, though. We'd have to VFX the entire thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.40,0:17:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,- 对 这里接受大家的各种想法 - 接受这个 你是个白痴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Right, this is a "yes and" room. - Oh, yes, and you're an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.90,0:17:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 不好的版本 是他把水变成葡萄酒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. Uh, the bad version is he turns water into wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.32,0:17:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,暂时反过来想一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Playing a quick game of opposites here, what if...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.36,0:18:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不做那么恶劣的事情怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it was something not fucking terrible?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,要是祖国人飞到世界上 所有的主要圣地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like, what if Homelander flew into all the major holy sites in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.17,0:18:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,让人们见到新上帝本尊呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let the people meet their new god in person, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.59,0:18:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,跟上帝拍自拍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Selfies with God.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.84,0:18:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,为了加强效果 我们可以让他 坐在圣殿山上的一个宝座上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pitching off of that, we could put him on a throne on the Temple Mount.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.97,0:18:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,用这个景象做海报就行 阿门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is your poster right there. Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.97,0:18:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.31,0:18:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,阐明一下 祖国人完全是神\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And for the record, Homelander is 100% God,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.81,0:18:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,但难道不会有人觉得他不是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}um, but won't some people say he's not?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.52,0:18:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,祖国人信仰者会为祖国人教会 带来大笔收入\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, a Homelander church would bring in Homelander box office.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.78,0:18:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们向上帝祈祷求助 上帝在回应\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We prayed to God for help. He's answering.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.74,0:18:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好像“边炮”说得有道理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Looks like Firecrotch has a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.20,0:18:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- 不好意思 - 没说你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Excuse me? - The other Firecrotch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.70,0:18:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,副总统女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Madam Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.95,0:18:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,因为根据这项即时民意调查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because according to the snap poll here,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.79,0:18:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,只有22%的美国人 会接受祖国人做唯一的真神\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}only 22% of Americans would even accept Homelander as their one true God,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.33,0:18:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说 让七成的人相信是非常困难的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}making a real uphill battle to get him into the 70s,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.38,0:18:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,而他需要七成\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which is where he'd need to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.88,0:18:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我得说 你们这些超人类只看重数字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, I'd say it's all about numbers with you suits,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.80,0:18:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 沃特加频道从来都不公布数字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but Vought Plus never releases any.
