Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.07,0:25:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,（《超级七人队新纪元》）
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.74,0:25:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,这部电影很烂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This movie was shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.53,0:25:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我确实考虑让你退我钱来着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I did consider asking you for my money back.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.04,0:25:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我不总是喜欢你的选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't always approve of the choices you made,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.66,0:25:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但我一直都为你感到骄傲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I was always proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.67,0:25:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,也许在你退出超级七人队时更加骄傲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe even more proud when you quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.42,0:25:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么离开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why did you leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.01,0:26:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你妈初遇时 我正在萨尔瓦多执行传教的任务\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The first time I saw your mother was on a church mission. El Salvador.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.39,0:26:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们那时很年轻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We were young.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.27,0:26:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,想要拯救世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wanted to save the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.02,0:26:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,有了你 我们很幸福\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We were so happy when you came along.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.90,0:26:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你妈很确定给你注射五号\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And your mom was dead certain that giving you V was...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.45,0:26:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,会给你更美好的生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}gonna give you a better life.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.24,0:26:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,比投币电话修理员…能给你的生活强\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Better than a pay phone repairman could give you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.41,0:26:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,她对我说：“你知道我们如何 才能真正改变世界吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She asked me, "Do you know how we can really change the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.25,0:26:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,答案就是养育超级英雄”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Raise a superhero."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.13,0:26:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你当时同意了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, you-you got on board?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.55,0:26:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,直到后来她开始告诉你 你是上帝的选民\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Until she started telling you you were chosen by God.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.22,0:26:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,问题是 你相信她的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And th-the thing is, you believed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.43,0:26:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,然后 她相信这些话 而我…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then she believed it, and I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.77,0:26:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我无法继续对你说谎 于是我就离开了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I couldn't keep lying to you, so I left.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.40,0:26:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你甚至都没跟我联系 - 联系你做什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You never even reached out. - To do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.36,0:26:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,粉碎你的梦想 继续对你说谎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shatter your dreams? Keep lying to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.61,0:26:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,怎样都行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd have taken either.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.90,0:26:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时是需要你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I needed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.58,0:27:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我能回到过去 做出改变 我会的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I could go back and change things, I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.12,0:27:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该陪在你身边 为你挺身而出\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I should have been there for you. Should have stood up for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.88,0:27:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我离开了 我很抱歉 安妮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry I left, Annie.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.84,0:27:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我们家人就这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It runs in the family, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.55,0:27:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么意思  - 我那天情绪失控了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What do you mean? - I flipped out the other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.81,0:27:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我抛下了一个自己很爱的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I ditched someone I really love.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.19,0:27:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他就像…我全心全意地爱着他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's like he's, um... it's like he's my heart walking on the outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.98,0:27:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 如果他们伤害他 我就无法… - 嘿 安妮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- and if they got to him, I couldn't-- - Annie.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.03,0:27:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我们爱的人不是弱点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The people we love aren't a weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.86,0:27:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他们是我们奋战的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're the reason that we fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.21,0:27:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我跟他谈谈可以吗  - 当然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Hey, is it all right if I talk to him? - Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.17,0:28:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不过…先敲门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh, j-just... knock first.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.47,0:28:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我好不容易学到的教训\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I learned that lesson the hard way.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.86,0:28:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好 实验室在这边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. The lab is this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.11,0:28:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,真他妈的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fucking hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.49,0:28:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,尸体在这里很长时间了 不是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They've been here a minute, haven't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.58,0:28:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,几十年了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.16,0:28:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,猎人 看他们的刀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hunters. Look at their knives.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.17,0:28:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人互相残杀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These men, they killed each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.00,0:28:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这里确实有怪物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What if there is a monster here
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.63,0:28:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但就是我们自己呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but it's us?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.88,0:28:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,法兰奇 你在胡说些什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What the fuck are you on about, Frenchie?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.18,0:28:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,弓形虫病\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Toxoplasmosis.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.14,0:28:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一种猫屎里的寄生虫 能感染人类\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a parasite in cat shit. It can infect humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.18,0:28:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,它会引起人类暴怒的反应\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Makes them react with explosive anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.56,0:28:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为我们吃猫屎吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You think we ate cat shit?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.98,0:28:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,吃 不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ate? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.65,0:28:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,如果一代五号渗入地下水 它就可能使植物发生突变\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If the V1 spilled into the groundwater, it could mutate th-the plants.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.40,0:29:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,它们的孢子令我们满心愤怒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Their spores fills us with rage,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.61,0:29:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我们互相谋杀 然后 一下子…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we murder each other, and voilà...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.07,0:29:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我们成了这些藤蔓的食物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...we're plant food for these vines.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.45,0:29:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,所以就像《最后生还者》\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, so like The Last of Us?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.41,0:29:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,不 那部剧就是《行尸走肉》加蘑菇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, that is just The Walking Dead with mushrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.96,0:29:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,死掉的露营者 动物 这些猎人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The dead campers, the animals, these hunters.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.34,0:29:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 你们都看见 自己的行为多么怪异了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Surely, you all see how strangely you've been acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.96,0:29:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们怪异  我可没少看见你吸完可卡因的怪样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Us? I've seen you blow cocaine up your dick hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.05,0:29:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 你说得有道理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait. You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.22,0:29:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,几十年来 我大量使用毒品\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The copious amount of drugs I've taken for decades
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.64,0:29:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定改变了我大脑的运作机制\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}has surely altered my brain chemistry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.31,0:29:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我才没受影响\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's why I'm not affected.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.52,0:29:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,看来做瘾君子总算是有点好处了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Guess being a junkie was good for something after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.56,0:29:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,罗密欧和朱丽叶\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Romeo and fucking Juliet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.44,0:29:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你们俩在这场战争中幸存下来 顶多相处六个月就会分开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You two survive this war, I give you six months, tops.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.28,0:29:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,真他妈的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well fucking well.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.00,0:30:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's fucking go.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.01,0:30:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你们要去哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wh-Wh... Wh-Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.30,0:30:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- 去干掉那些傻屌 - 你们会害死我们的 蠢货\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- To top those cunts. - You'll get us killed, you fucking idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.14,0:30:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 你们现在脑子都不清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Neither of you are thinking straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.06,0:30:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,法兰奇 别用枪指着我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get that fucking gun out of my face, Frenchie.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.43,0:30:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,小子 那玩意儿对付不了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That ain't gonna do shit to me, sonny.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.43,0:30:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是没用 但我会对付你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, but I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.69,0:30:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,祖国人和士兵男孩杀你们 然后再杀我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Homelander and Soldier Boy kill you, then kill us.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.40,0:30:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那样的话 如果这里有一代五号 就会落入祖国人手中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then, if there's any V1 here, it's Homelander's.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.32,0:30:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这样你的家人会安全吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Does that make your family safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.07,0:30:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你追求的复仇吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that the revenge you seek?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.53,0:30:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这会为贝嘉寻得正义吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Does that make things right for Becca?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.00,0:30:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.38,0:30:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,趁我们还没互相残杀 或被那两个超人类杀掉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We must hurry before we tear each other apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.96,0:30:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,得赶快行动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or the Supes do.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.68,0:30:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那计划是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, what's the plan? God!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.59,0:30:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 天哪  - 搞什么 法兰奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Ugh! - The fuck, Frenchie?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.05,0:30:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这是鹿尿 猎人用它吸引猎物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's deer urine. Hunters use it to attract prey,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.64,0:30:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们会用它掩盖气味 不让祖国人闻到我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but we will use it to hide our scent from Homelander.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.35,0:31:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是敢往我身上喷那玩意儿 我就他妈的把你脑袋揪掉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You spray that shit on me, and I'll rip your fucking head off.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.44,0:31:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不会靠鹿尿救我们的命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I ain't counting on no goddamn deer piss to save our asses.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.03,0:31:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这是科学嘛 兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's just science, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.49,0:31:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,射精时 你的身体会损失阳气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When you jizz, masculine vitality leaves your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.24,0:31:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这么重要的东西 得留在体内 对吗 玄色\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Got to hold that shit in, right, Noir?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.79,0:31:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,对吗 玄色\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right, Noir?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.54,0:31:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,去…你妈的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fu-fu-fu-fuck you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.46,0:31:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,看来你按错了按钮 小兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Looks like you hit the wrong button there, broseph.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.58,0:31:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,贱…贱人说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}B-B-Bitch says what?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.92,0:31:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.34,0:31:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.43,0:31:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just want to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.64,0:31:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,哇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.89,0:31:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,上面没有你的照片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your picture was never up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.43,0:31:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.35,0:31:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,（采婷保湿乳）
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.85,0:31:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 我是说 那样挺好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good. I mean, uh, yeah, no, that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.69,0:31:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我的墙上不挂叛徒的照片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't put traitors on my wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.07,0:31:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,知道吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.03,0:31:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他们说我的那些事 都不是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}what they say about me, none of it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.61,0:31:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的是靠给人吹箫进入超级七人队\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you mean the part that you blew your way into The Seven
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.87,0:31:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,还是你是贩运儿童的恐怖分子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or that you're a terrorist who traffics children?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.12,0:31:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你是肯定 不会进我货车的后车厢了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So that's, like, a hard no on getting into the back of my van?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.87,0:32:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 听着 梅森\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, look, Mason,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.17,0:32:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你每天去祖国人学院上学\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you go to school at Homelander Academy
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.38,0:32:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,回家刷几千条抖音视频\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you come home and you watch thousands of TikToks every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.38,0:32:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,事实怎么能 跟你接触的虚假信息竞争\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How is the truth supposed to compete with that?
