Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.43,0:32:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,对此 你可以继续表现得像个混蛋 或者 我们可以谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so you can keep being an asshole about it or, you know, we can also talk about it.
