Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.11,0:34:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但这是个玩笑 对吗  告诉我这是个玩笑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it's a joke, right? Tell me it's a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.66,0:34:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她是我女儿 - 你女儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- She's my daughter. - Your daughter?
