Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.59,0:37:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么 你觉得这个世界需要更多 长生不老的超人类傻屌吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What? You think the world needs more immortal cunts, do you?
