Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.37,0:38:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,想知道个小秘密吗 布彻尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Want to know a little secret, Butcher?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.75,0:38:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,得知你快死的时候 我心里高兴着呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I cheered when I found out that you were dying,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.25,0:38:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,因为至少我们终于 不用再忍受你那惨兮兮的模样了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}'cause at least we'd finally be done with your miserable ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.67,0:38:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前总对他们说：“别放弃布彻尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, I used to say to these guys, "Don't give up on Butcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.80,0:38:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他内心有善良的一面 只是表现出来很难” 我是错的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's good in him fighting to get out." I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.34,0:38:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你内心还有人性 也已经消逝了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If there was anything human in there, it's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.97,0:38:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你的胸膛里只有八爪鱼一般的 老二藤蔓 你就是个怪物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Underneath that chestful of octo-cocks, you are just a fucking monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.14,0:38:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我更喜欢这个样子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, maybe I like it better that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.93,0:38:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,那个寄生虫不仅在你体内 你就是寄生虫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That parasite's not just in you. It is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.31,0:38:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你就是癌症 - 小点声\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You're the cancer. - Lower your voices.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.86,0:38:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟祖国人一样坏 也许更坏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are just as bad as Homelander, maybe worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.40,0:38:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我不容许你害我们跟你一起玩完\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I'm not gonna let you drag us all down with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.44,0:38:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你又能怎样呢 小子  - 我要杀了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- And what you gonna do about it? - I'll fucking kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.95,0:38:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不 小心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.41,0:38:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,喜美子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kimiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.45,0:38:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,请冷静\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please. Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.00,0:39:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过了 我不是你的小宠物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I told you I'm not your pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.38,0:39:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我受够听你指挥了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm done following your commands.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.09,0:39:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,喜美子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Kimiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.97,0:39:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,动手吧 MM\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, M.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.26,0:39:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 要是布彻尔允许的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, if Butcher will let you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.31,0:39:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 请住手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everybody, please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.62,0:39:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你这是要去哪呀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oi! Where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.34,0:39:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mon coeur. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.76,0:39:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,别…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.85,0:39:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,强悍个狗屁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tough guy, my ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.31,0:39:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么  - 你 你的那一套\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What? - You, your whole bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.77,0:40:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,勇气和荣誉那一套\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This whole "guts and glory" thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.60,0:40:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,一派胡言 真是个笑话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What a fucking joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.94,0:40:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我读过你的机密文档\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I read your classified file.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.19,0:40:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你哥在登陆安齐奥时作战英勇 获得了银星勋章\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your brother won a Silver Star for bravery at Anzio,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.19,0:40:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,因此 你恳求父亲靠贿赂 为你争取到参加沃特博士试验的机会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and that's what made you beg your father to buy you a spot in Dr. Vought's trials.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.32,0:40:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,因为看见哥哥独自享有所有的荣耀 让你难受得要死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because it killed you to see your brother dripping in all that glory,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.91,0:40:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,让你相形之下更显得软弱无能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}making you look all the more feeble in comparison.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.00,0:40:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,关于我 你一无所知\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't know shit about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.38,0:40:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.63,0:40:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道他们想给你注射五号时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know that when they tried to inject you with the V,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.34,0:40:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你吓得要死 他们只好把你绑在床上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you were so fucking petrified that they had to strap you to the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.14,0:40:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你都吓尿了 大声叫妈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you pissed yourself, crying for your mommy
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.68,0:40:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,像个爱发牢骚 被宠坏的富家子弟 那就是你的本来面目\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}like the whiny, spoiled little rich boy that you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.27,0:40:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你的父母给了你一切 可你根本不值一文\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They gave you the world, and you, you deserve nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.03,0:40:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪 这是什么鬼地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, Christ. What's this shithole now?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.66,0:40:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.17,0:41:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,干得漂亮\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.88,0:41:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我30秒之内就会出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll be out of here in 30 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.46,0:41:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,也许出不来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe. Maybe not.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.05,0:41:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是浓缩铀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's enriched uranium.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.59,0:41:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会把超人类关进里面 看我们能否在原子弹爆炸后存活下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They'd stick us Supes in there to see if we could survive an atomic bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.84,0:41:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,普通人几分钟内就会死掉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, for a normal joe, they'd be dead in minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.10,0:41:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不过对你来说 那就跟胃肠炎差不多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but for you, it's a stomach flu.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.27,0:41:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 祝你好运\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good luck, though,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.98,0:41:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,一边要从防超人类舱里出来 一边大量流血\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}getting out of a Supe-proof cell while you're bleeding out of your ass.
