Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.12,0:41:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我要毁掉找到的任何一代五号 你个爱操男人的软蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna go destroy any V1 that I find, you Triple Crown cock jockey.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.87,0:41:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,- 为什么  - 你不明白是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Why? - You don't get it, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.92,0:41:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你不明白我有多受不了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How much I can't fucking stand you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.63,0:42:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,休伊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hughie.
