Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.28,0:43:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,要是真的注射了一代五号 你觉得自己就成神了 是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you do get the juice in you, you think that makes you a god, don't you?
