Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.12,0:48:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你还他妈的恨我 不是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You still fucking hate me, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.79,0:48:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这个生物心里只有憎恨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This creature is nothing but hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.29,0:48:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们憎恨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He makes us hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.21,0:48:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是他造成了这一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's the cause of all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.17,0:48:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.38,0:48:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,只有你才能了结这一切 了结他的痛苦吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are the only one who can end it. Put a stop to his misery.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.97,0:49:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,了结他的痛苦 不 那可不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Put him out of his misery? No, no. God, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.18,0:49:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我喜欢他这个样子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I like him like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.02,0:49:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,去你妈的 贱人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, fuck you, bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.98,0:49:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我不值得我所拥有的东西吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, I didn't deserve what I got, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.82,0:49:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,去你妈的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fuck you. Fuck you!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.78,0:49:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我风范不减当年 所以去你妈的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}'Cause I still got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.24,0:49:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我一如既往地强大  我他妈的比你强\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got all of it. I fucking won!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.50,0:49:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,要是你不杀了他 我们都会死的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you won't kill him, all of us will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.05,0:49:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道奎因为什么恨你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know why Quinn hates you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.34,0:49:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.43,0:49:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他看到你的真面目\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because he sees you for what you really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.18,0:49:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,他曾是真正的士兵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was a real soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.14,0:49:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,而你只是个穿着制服装装样子的男孩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were just a boy playing dress-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.60,0:49:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不过你成了英雄 他却只能这样活着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you got to be the hero while he got to be this.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.35,0:49:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,真是毫无公正可言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, where's the justice in that?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.36,0:49:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你在那上面才对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It should be you up there. - Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.11,0:49:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,- 闭嘴 - 这都应该是你的痛苦才对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It should be your pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.94,0:49:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你不过就是个懦夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are nothing but a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.74,0:49:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我让你闭嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said shut your fucking mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.05,0:50:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,休伊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hughie?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.18,0:50:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.43,0:50:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.02,0:50:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我也很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.39,0:51:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,妈的 对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fuck. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.64,0:51:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我太抱歉了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm so fucking sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.40,0:52:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我吃过的最好吃的酸奶牛肉了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well... That was the best stroganoff I have ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.95,0:52:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定不是 不过感谢你的好心夸奖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It definitely wasn't, but that's kind of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.37,0:52:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你想说什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have something you want to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.83,0:52:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.67,0:52:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你想再说一次吗  - 我很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You want to try that again? - I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.38,0:52:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,很好 不过你20岁之前都被禁足了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good. But you're grounded till you're 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.26,0:52:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,禁足到30岁还差不多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mm, more like 30.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.59,0:52:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望我们会再见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hope we see each other again.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.97,0:52:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.86,0:52:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,安妮 别犯我犯过的错误\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Annie? Don't make the same mistake I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.65,0:52:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,别放弃自己爱的人 好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't give up on the people you love, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.19,0:53:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,一代五号不在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The V1 wasn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.36,0:54:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Were you...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.07,0:54:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你在哭吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Were you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.04,0:54:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,快下手吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just fucking do it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.91,0:54:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.53,0:54:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,要不是你挺身而出 我们是出不来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We wouldn't have made it out if you hadn't stepped up.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.83,0:54:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,知道嘛 负责…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, well, taking charge...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.58,0:55:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是我做过的最糟糕的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...was the most horrible thing I've ever done.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.84,0:55:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,永远都别再让我负责了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never let me do it again. Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.34,0:55:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 我叫你瘾君子软蛋来着\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry I called you a feckless junkie man-whore.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.89,0:55:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我没记得你这样说我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't remember you calling me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.64,0:55:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,没有吗 我还以为我说了呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't? I thought I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.60,0:55:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你没说错 我以前确实是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're not wrong. I was, once.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.57,0:55:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 我现在戒掉了 你让我变成什么样我都做得到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I am clean now. And I can be whatever you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.87,0:55:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想改变你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't want to change you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.25,0:55:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,是…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's that...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.13,0:55:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我在努力改变自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...I'm trying to change myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.00,0:55:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在能说话了是因为…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The reason I can speak now, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.88,0:55:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,是因为我很努力地卸掉情感上的包袱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it's because I did so much work to let go of my... chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.43,0:55:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,可你热爱情感上的包袱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The thing is... you love chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.18,0:56:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你擅长应对它们 这倒没关系 不过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You thrive in it. Which is fine, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.56,0:56:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能把那些包袱再扛起来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...I can't go back to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.24,0:56:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们之间算什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, where does that leave us?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.77,0:56:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 我不应该离开你的 我应该待在这里的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry. I shouldn't have left you. I should've been here.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.64,0:56:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,其实 我很开心你不在 错过今天是件大好事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Actually, I'm so, so glad you weren't. Super good day to miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.21,0:57:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,听着 伙计 我之前说的那些鬼话…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Listen, mate. That shite I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.92,0:57:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 别告诉我那不是真心话 好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey. Don't tell me you didn't mean it, a'ight?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.00,0:57:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我说的每个字都是发自内心的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}'Cause I sure as hell meant every fucking word I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.63,0:57:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们之间有问题了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, we got a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.14,0:57:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,没有 伙计 没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We cool, man. We cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.23,0:57:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.53,0:57:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,思考\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.28,0:57:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,“好戏”要开场了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, the shit show is on.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.57,0:57:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,从东海岸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}? From sea ?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.53,0:57:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,（神父大人即将宣布“重大消息”）
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.58,0:57:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,到西海岸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}? to shining sea ?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.54,0:57:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,美国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}? America ?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.21,0:57:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.55,0:57:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,兄弟姐妹们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brothers and sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.85,0:58:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,兄弟姐妹们 我们今日得以见证\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brothers and sisters, we are truly, truly fortunate
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.60,0:58:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,实在是万幸之事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to bear witness on this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.10,0:58:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,因为今天是撒马利亚人怀抱 史上最伟大的一天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because today... is the greatest day in the history of Samaritan's Embrace.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.40,0:58:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,- 能给我一句阿门吗  - 阿门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Can I get an amen? -  Amen!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.49,0:58:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我爱这种场面 很爱 - 250年前…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, I love all this, love,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.03,0:58:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你不相信耶稣什么的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but don't you believe in Jesus or whatever?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.41,0:58:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我信过 现在我信的是祖国人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I did. Now I believe in Homelander.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.66,0:58:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,她在说谎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.83,0:58:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- 可不是嘛 - 什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No shit. - Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.29,0:58:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不过今天 兄弟姐妹们 今天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But today, brothers and sisters, today,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.04,0:58:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我们让美国重回正轨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we set America back on its true course.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.17,0:58:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,从今天开始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Starting today,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.72,0:58:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,兄弟姐妹们 我们致力于 一项神圣的重塑之伟业\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}brothers and sisters, we commit ourselves to a divine rebranding.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.68,0:58:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们将成为有信仰的爱国者\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We will be patriots of faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.52,0:58:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们将实现国父们的梦想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We will fulfill our Founding Fathers' dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.52,0:58:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- 我们会的  - 就在今天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Today,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.82,0:58:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,从今天开始 撒玛利亚人怀抱变为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}starting today, Samaritan's Embrace becomes
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.57,0:58:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,美国民主教会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the Democratic Church of America.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.62,0:59:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,现在来分享 他对我们新教会的神圣计划…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And here, to share his holy plan for our new church,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.04,0:59:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他不只是个男人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he is not just a man...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.38,0:59:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,他不只是个超人类\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...he's not just a super man...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.18,0:59:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他是我主的先知\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...he is the Prophet of the Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.68,0:59:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他是美国的先知\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He is the Prophet of America!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.23,0:59:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他就是先知祖国人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He is the Prophet Homelander!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.63,0:59:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,祖国人…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Homelander! Home--
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.02,1:00:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,（根据炸药娱乐漫画系列改编 创作 加思恩尼斯）
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.10,1:00:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,（绘制 达里克罗伯逊）
